{
  "stem": "9.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "It proves that a human being can adapt, and necessity is the mother of inventions.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "You do help yourself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father's name was Eisig Lewin, E-I-S-I-G, Eisig.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "L-E-W-I-N was his last name, and that was the family name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My birth date is June the 8th, 1927.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you have to realize I was a little girl going to public school during the day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Afterwards, there were all the lessons and activities.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the winter, I did an awful lot of ice skating.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was a very good ice skater, figure ice skater.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then I would play with friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On the weekends, there were outings, some of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, our-- my parents were religious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That meant that on Saturday I couldn't do very much.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I-- they went the services.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was hanging around outside with other kids making all the noise.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But afterwards, we had to go home and eat the daily meal, the dinner, that was served in the middle of the day.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "On Saturday, we weren't allowed to light the fire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "As a result, we ate what you called cholent, C-H-O-L-E-N-T.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "What it means basically is any food that's available, it's put into baker's oven on Friday and cooks very, very slowly overnight.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And Saturday, after services, I would be-- they sent me to pick up the pot, the hot pot, and I brought it, and that's what we ate.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Into the cholent, usually luckily what was available at that time, there were a lot of potatoes, some kind of bones, a piece of meat, and beans and vegetables, which isn't much different than we have today, certain one-pot meals.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But potatoes were the-- was the staple of Poland, because we had a lot of it.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
